# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FLUJO 2 · ERRORES DE VALIDACIÓN DE INPUT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [REG-10] Sin name ni firstName/lastName (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @AssertTrue isNameProvided() falla: se requiere name O (firstName + lastName).
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identification": "9000000001",
  "email": "sinnombre@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-11] Email con formato inválido (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @Email de Bean Validation rechaza el formato antes de llegar a EmailValidator.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Formato",
  "identification": "9000000002",
  "email": "no-es-un-email",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-12] Position con valor fuera del patrón (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @Pattern(regexp="(?i)^(Portero|Defensa|Volante|Delantero)$") rechaza el valor.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Posicion",
  "identification": "9000000003",
  "email": "test.posicion@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Mediocampista"
}

###

### [REG-13] Sin userType (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @NotBlank en userType — el normalizador nunca llega a ejecutarse.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Sin Tipo",
  "identification": "9000000004",
  "email": "test.sintipo@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-14] Password menor a 8 caracteres (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @Size(min=8) en password.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Password",
  "identification": "9000000005",
  "email": "test.password@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "corta",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-15] Árbitro sin licenseNumber (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @NotBlank en licenseNumber del RefereeRequest.
POST {{host}}/referees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Árbitro Sin Licencia",
  "email": "sinlicencia@gmail.com",
  "password": "Techcup123*"
}

###

### [REG-16] jerseyNumber fuera de rango (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# @Min(1) @Max(99) en jerseyNumber.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Dorsal",
  "identification": "9000000006",
  "email": "test.dorsal@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero",
  "jerseyNumber": 150
}

