# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FLUJO 3 · ERRORES DE VALIDACIONES DE NEGOCIO
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [REG-17] Email ya registrado (esperado: 409 Conflict)
# existsByEmail() devuelve true → BusinessRuleException "El correo '...' ya está registrado."
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicado Email",
  "identification": "9000000010",
  "email": "carlos.estudiante@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-18] Identificación ya registrada (esperado: 409 Conflict)
# existsByIdentification() devuelve true → BusinessRuleException "La identificación '...' ya está registrada."
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicado Cedula",
  "identification": "1000100001",
  "email": "nuevo.unico@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-19] STUDENT con email de dominio incorrecto (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# StudentEmailValidator requiere @mail.escuelaing.edu.co — Gmail no es válido.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Estudiante Gmail",
  "identification": "9000000011",
  "email": "estudiante.gmail@gmail.com",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "STUDENT",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-20] TEACHER con email de dominio de estudiante (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# StaffEmailValidator requiere @escuelaing.edu.co — @mail.escuelaing.edu.co no es válido.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Profesor Mail Incorrecto",
  "identification": "9000000012",
  "email": "profesor.mail@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "TEACHER",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-21] RELATIVE con email institucional (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# GmailValidator requiere @gmail.com — email institucional no es válido para familiares.
POST {{host}}/players/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Familiar Email Incorrecto",
  "identification": "9000000013",
  "email": "familiar.inst@mail.escuelaing.edu.co",
  "password": "Techcup123*",
  "userType": "RELATIVE",
  "position": "Portero"
}

###

### [REG-22] Árbitro con licencia duplicada (esperado: 409 Conflict)
# existsByLicenseNumber() devuelve true → BusinessRuleException
POST {{host}}/referees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Árbitro Licencia Duplicada",
